Druids are magicians, bards, rangers and others who draw their power from nature.

The Druid battles the Hydra in the Hollow of the Deep

The druid uses a wand, mace or staff to channel their magic

The druid's power generally can be divided between gathering the essence of lunar and solar energies (although other, stranger variants (extraterrestrial druidry) may occur)

Druid's can guide and hasten the processes of nature channel more energies
More powerful spellcasters can generate more complex energies- such as from earth and metal elements.


Solar essence: Bright and warm, solar essence is superior for combating Abyssal opponents

Lunar essence: Dark and cool, lunar essence is excellent at combating Infernal opponents

